reviews.review_text:
Rough Show Weather had a lot to do with it, but not much here.
No Highlights

As time goes by It seems that as time goes by listener's expectations of how it should sound tend to to be a bit high - back in the 80"s, if I got a recording that sounded like this (would have been on cassette) I would have been like "Wow dude check it out this shit is awesome!" I'm giving it stars because even on their worst day these boys were better than anything else happening in the summer of '84
